title: Lode Runner On-Line - The Mad Monks' Revenge CD
description:
This is the Full CD of the 1995 PC Game: Lode Runner On-Line: The Mad Monks' Revenge

The CD is a multi-track image, which I have put in the more common BIN/CUE format and compressed into a SFX archive to make it easier to seed.

The Readme.txt should give you all of the information that is needed to run the game.

I have also included a custom modification that I have recently made.

Enjoy!
Teslaman
